collectors.titleDetails: (2 total Queries, 2 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: SELECT pi.action_date,pi.property_id, pi.property_name, pi.city, pi.property_area, pi.property_size, pi.beds, pi.baths, pi.price, pi.is_occupied, pi.floor_plan, pi.phone_number, pi.property_address, pi.level, pi.email, pi.description, pi.amenities, pi.purpose_code, ppc.look_up_name AS purpose_name, pi.property_type_code, ptc.look_up_name AS property_type_name, pi.descriptive_status_code, dsc.look_up_name AS descriptive_status_name, pi.property_status_code, psc.look_up_name AS property_status_name FROM tbl_property_info as pi INNER JOIN tbl_look_up AS psc ON pi.property_status_code = psc.look_up_id INNER JOIN tbl_look_up AS ppc ON pi.purpose_code = ppc.look_up_id INNER JOIN tbl_look_up AS dsc ON pi.descriptive_status_code = dsc.look_up_id INNER JOIN tbl_look_up AS ptc ON pi.property_type_code = ptc.look_up_id ORDER BY pi.property_id
